data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR DREAM POOL HOME with over $100K worth of upgrades and one of the largest corner lots in the neighborhood! CLOSE IN THE NEXT 30 DAYS USING MY PREFERRED LENDER AND WE CAN COVER YOUR APPRAISAL, WAIVE THE PROCESSING FEE, AND OFFER A COMPETITIVE RATE FOR THE BUYER! Sit back and relax while you enjoy a oversized corner lot with plenty of privacy for you and your guests and ample space for your pets! Complete with an outdoor oasis featuring an inground salt-water pool, pergola, and extended paver deck.  Get ready to be swept up in perfection by this just over 2-year-old new beauty presents with high ceilings, crown moldings, and eight-foot doors. Nothing has been overlooked when it comes to the high-performance window treatments, smart cooking appliances, dual ovens for the chef of the house, induction stovetop, dual zone climate control system, and storage capacity in every conceivable space for the overall smooth living goal of life. Distinct and defined areas of enjoyment is the strength of this floorplan with the entire lower level extending from a large master bedroom overlooking the pool that continues into a a large master bathroom featuring jack and jill double sinks, a walk-in glass shower connected to an incredible oversize soaker tub to end the day. A large walk-in closet that opens into the laundry room for quick access. All upstairs bedrooms are spacious with one shared bathroom, and a bedroom with a private bathroom for your guests. A bonus room equipped with French doors that can be used as a fifth bedroom or private office space. With a spacious, open floor plan this home is great for entertaining family and friends. This innate coastal vibe is the result of the use of sun-bleached colors of the natural shades of blue and sand. This is a dog walking, friendly faces neighborhood you will love. Conveniently located in the heart of Wesley Chapel close to Wiregrass Mall, two major hospitals, Tampa Premium Outlets, Advent Health Center Ice rink, WCAA District Park, and the best dining, shopping, and entertainment. Top-rated schools are within reach! Commuting is a breeze with quick access to SR56 and I75. Schedule your private showing today!!
